- By writing tests before building each part of your app—and then creating just enough code to pass them—you’ll learn how TDD leads to clean, reliable, and maintainable software.
- Percival takes you through a practical, end-to-end example of web development using Python 3.14 and Django 5.
- Along the way, you’ll explore tools like Selenium, JavaScript, Git, and mocking, and discover how TDD supports better design decisions, encourages continuous improvement, and instills confidence in your codebase.
